title: Frank Lloyd Wright Coonley Playhouse Eyeglass Case
description:
Keep your sunglasses, reading glasses, or eyeglasses safe inside your favorite art! This stunning Frank Lloyd Wright sunglass and eyeglass case is beautifully designed to keep your glasses protected in style. These cases feature a flat fold design, extra soft interior, magnet snap closure, and a thumb notch for easy opening.

  • Dimensions: 2.6 x 6.3 in.
